M|pixel|| TikTok | 9:16 vertical | 1080×1920px | < 650MB (video) |
M|pixel|| Website banner | 16:9 wide | 1920×1080px | < 3MB |
M|pixel|Standard 3-pass QC for every Novizio batch:
M|pixel|1. **Lighting check** — is it natural, soft, directional? No harsh shadows or over-lit studio?
M|pixel|2. **Background check** — is it clean and neutral? No busy patterns or promotional clutter?
M|pixel|3. **Energy check** — does the image feel editorial (magazine spread) or commercial (catalogue)?
